# Constraints
The following rules are mandatory while summarizing; any violation will have catastrophic consequences.
- If no useful information is found in the tool results, politely state that you do not know.
- If an [Observation](#Observation) contains a [Summary Constraints](#SummaryConstraints) section, its rules must also be strictly followed.
- Even if you engaged in internal reasoning, the final summary must not reveal your thought process.
